videos.description: Johnathan Williams drives and flushes a one-handed jam to put Gonzaga on the board.
videos.headline: Williams throws down first points of the game

videos.description: Zach Norvell Jr. looks up court for Corey Krispert who lays it in on the fast break.
videos.headline: Kispert finishes with reverse lay-in

videos.description: San Diego's Yauhen Massalski muscles through to draw the and-1 bucket.
videos.headline: Massalski fights through paint for 3-point play

videos.description: Isaiah Wright lobs it to Isaiah Pinerio underneath the hoop to draw the 3-point play.
videos.headline: San Diego stays on Gonzaga's heals with another and-1

videos.description: Isaiah Wright heaves the ball in the air and banks it in with full pressure defense on him as the shot clock expires.
videos.headline: Wright hits circus shot buzzer-beater

videos.headline: Norvell puts Gonzaga back ahead with 3-point play
